Kelvingrove Park, Glasgow
March contest - 1st Clydebank, 2nd Scottish CWS, 3rd Scottish Gas Board. Best section 2 band - Whitburn. Best section 3 band - Croy Parish. Best section 4 band - Duntocher. Best baritone - J.McMillan Scottish CWS. Best cornet - T.Clucas, best soprano - W.Bonowski, best flugal - W.McNeill, best bass trombone - D.Lunn - all from Clydebank Burgh. 16 bands competed.
